    <h1>About AgriLinkHub</h1>
    <p>AgriLinkHub was founded with a vision to revolutionize the agricultural industry by creating a seamless connection between all stakeholders in the farming ecosystem.</p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Started in 2023, AgriLinkHub emerged from the need to address the challenges faced by farmers, suppliers, and buyers in traditional agricultural markets. We recognized the potential of technology to bridge gaps and create more efficient, transparent, and sustainable agricultural practices.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Our diverse team consists of agricultural experts, technology professionals, and business strategists who are passionate about supporting the farming community.</p>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Transparency</strong>: Open and honest transactions</li>
      <li><strong>Sustainability</strong>: Promoting eco-friendly farming practices</li>
      <li><strong>Innovation</strong>: Leveraging technology for better outcomes</li>
      <li><strong>Community</strong>: Building strong relationships within the agricultural sector</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
